## Console Test (stake.com)

```javascript
// Test button click capture
const rows = [...document.querySelectorAll('table tr')].filter(tr => tr.querySelectorAll('td').length >= 5);
const btn = rows[0].querySelector('button');
btn.click();
setTimeout(() => {
    const iid = new URL(location.href).searchParams.get('iid');
    console.log('iid:', iid ? '✅ ' + iid : '❌ Not found');
    history.back();
}, 1000);
```

